{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji29","name":"毛泽东全集第29卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji29.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给蒋竹如的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给蒋竹如的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1950年8月10日）竹如兄："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七月三十一日来信收到。顷询革大，据称该校研究班九月间可收留若干人。似此，兄如有决心，并能吃苦（该校火【伙】食不大好），可以来此入学研究。大作同时收到，甚谢！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顺颂教祺！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八月十日[1]蒋竹如，毛泽东在湖南省立第一师范学校读书时的同学。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":8,"day":10}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":81,"page_end":81},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}